  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Ranged Tactics Toolbox pg. 18</em></p>\n<h3><span title=\"PFS Legal\">[PFS]</span> Statistics</h3>\n<p><strong>Cost</strong> 400 gp <strong>Weight</strong> 12 lbs.</p>\n<p><strong>Damage</strong> 1d8 (small), 1d10 (medium); <strong>Critical</strong> 19-20/x2; <strong>Range</strong> 120 ft.; <strong>Type</strong> P; <strong>Special</strong> -</p>\n<p><strong>Category</strong> Ranged; <strong>Proficiency</strong> Exotic</p>\n<h3>Description</h3>\n<p>This heavy crossbow has a winch mounted below the stock. Up to 50 feet of silk rope can be wound onto the winch as a full-round action that provokes attacks of opportunity. The wound rope can be attached to a @Compendium[pf1.weapons-and-ammo.84twkW8rwnUEX4EY]{Barbed Bolt} or grappling bolt<sup>UE</sup> as part of a loading action. After firing such a bolt, the wielder can use the winch to retract the rope or pull herself along the rope if the bolt is secure. When used with a barbed bolt, the winch provides a +2 bonus on grapple combat maneuver checks to pull the target toward you. When used with a grappling bolt<sup>UE</sup>, the winch provides a +2 bonus on @Compendium[pf1.skills.xvua9V5Zggkc77Gt]{Climb} checks.</p>"
    },
